public class LMSRecommenderTester
extends javax.swing.JFrame

Main tester application GUI that provides the functionality to executes all LMSRecommender implementations. Furthermore it is possible to evaluate the recommender by a 'leave one out' or 'hold out'(Cross-Validation) evaluation. The GUI also shows the different source codes and related documentation each LMSRecommender. Note: These LMSRecommenders are CBR (Case based Reasoning) recommenders implemented for an e-learning environment like Learning Management Systems (LMS).

Version:
1.1
Author:
Tell Mueller-Pettenpohl
